statements: SELECT * FROM software_licenses;
SELECT software_name, license_key FROM software_licenses WHERE license_id = 1;
SELECT software_name, expiration_date FROM software_licenses WHERE expiration_date > NOW();
SELECT software_name, usage_info FROM software_licenses WHERE license_key = 'ABCDE1234';
SELECT * FROM software_licenses WHERE expiration_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31';
SELECT * FROM software_licenses WHERE software_name = 'ProductA';
SELECT software_name, expiration_date FROM software_licenses WHERE expiration_date > NOW();
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_licenses FROM software_licenses;
SELECT software_name, license_key FROM software_licenses ORDER BY expiration_date DESC;
SELECT license_id, software_name, usage_info FROM software_licenses WHERE software_name LIKE '%Software%' ORDER BY license_id ASC;
SELECT * FROM software_licenses
SELECT software_name, license_type FROM software_licenses ORDER BY license_id DESC
SELECT DISTINCT license_type FROM software_licenses
SELECT software_name, customer_id FROM software_licenses WHERE license_type = 'subscription'
SELECT license_id, license_start_date FROM software_licenses WHERE license_end_date IS NULL
SELECT * FROM usage_tracking WHERE license_id = 1234 AND user_id = 5678;
SELECT software_name, license_type FROM software_licenses WHERE customer_id = 9876 ORDER BY license_start_date DESC;
SELECT software_name, customer_id, license_type FROM software_licenses WHERE license_type = 'subscription' OR license_type = 'perpetual';
SELECT DISTINCT software_name FROM software_licenses WHERE license_start_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31';
SELECT software_name, COUNT(*) AS total_usage FROM software_licenses JOIN usage_tracking ON software_licenses.license_id = usage_tracking.license_id GROUP BY software_name ORDER BY total_usage DESC;
SELECT * FROM software_licenses;
SELECT software_name, company_name FROM software_licenses WHERE id = 1;
SELECT license_key, COUNT(license_key) AS total_usage FROM license_usage GROUP BY license_key;
SELECT * FROM license_compliance WHERE is_compliant = true;
SELECT software_name, company_name, usage_time FROM software_licenses INNER JOIN license_usage ON software_licenses.license_key = license_usage.license_key;
SELECT * FROM software_licenses ORDER BY company_name ASC, software_name DESC;
SELECT software_name, company_name, COUNT(*) AS total_usage FROM license_usage GROUP BY software_name, company_name;
SELECT sl.software_name, lc.is_compliant FROM software_licenses AS sl INNER JOIN license_compliance AS lc ON sl.license_key = lc.license_key WHERE lc.is_compliant = TRUE;
SELECT DISTINCT company_name FROM software_licenses;
SELECT lu.user_id, lu.usage_time, sl.software_name FROM license_usage AS lu INNER JOIN software_licenses AS sl ON lu.license_key = sl.license_key ORDER BY lu.usage_time DESC;
SELECT * FROM software_license;
SELECT customer_name, purchase_date FROM software_license WHERE customer_name = 'Alice';
SELECT customer_name, expiration_date FROM software_license ORDER BY expiration_date DESC;
SELECT customer_name, cost, currency FROM software_license JOIN license_cost ON software_license.id = license_cost.license_id;
SELECT customer.customer_name, software_usage.usage_date FROM customer JOIN software_usage ON customer.id = software_usage.license_id;
SELECT * FROM software_license WHERE customer_name = 'John Doe';
SELECT customer_name, purchase_date FROM software_license ORDER BY purchase_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM software_usage WHERE used_hours > 10 ORDER BY usage_date ASC;

SELECT customer.customer_name, software_license.license_key, license_cost.cost FROM customer JOIN software_license ON customer.id = software_license.id JOIN license_cost ON software_license.id = license_cost.license_id WHERE license_cost.cost > 100;
SELECT * FROM software_license WHERE purchase_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31';
SELECT * FROM SoftwareLicenses;
SELECT license_id, software_name, version FROM SoftwareLicenses WHERE expiration_date > '2022-12-31';
SELECT software_name, company FROM SoftwareLicenses ORDER BY company ASC;
SELECT * FROM UsageDetails WHERE usage_count > 100 ORDER BY usage_count DESC;
SELECT license_id, COUNT(usage_id) AS usage_count FROM LicenseUsage GROUP BY license_id;
SELECT * FROM SoftwareLicenses ORDER BY issue_date DESC, expiration_date ASC
SELECT software_name, version, company FROM SoftwareLicenses WHERE company='ABC Corp'
SELECT software_name, COUNT(license_id) AS total_licenses FROM SoftwareLicenses GROUP BY software_name HAVING total_licenses > 5
SELECT SoftwareLicenses.software_name, LicenseUsage.usage_date FROM SoftwareLicenses JOIN LicenseUsage ON SoftwareLicenses.license_id = LicenseUsage.license_id WHERE LicenseUsage.duration_hours > 10
SELECT * FROM UsageDetails WHERE usage_count BETWEEN 100 AND 500 ORDER BY detail_id DESC
